  "body": "In Helm 3.0.0 final, `helm package` appears to be stripping the comments out of the values file. This happens when the values file is parsed and then re-marshaled (since the Go YAML parser does not keep comments).\r\n\r\nTo reproduce:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ helm create foo\r\n$ helm package foo\r\n$ helm inspect values ./foo\r\n$ helm inspect values foo-0.1.0.tgz\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
